divs: Sighting Details My dog has a tendency to sit and whine while looking skyward when a UFO is in the area. Tonight for two hours whether inside or outside of our house he sat and whined at the sky or the ceiling inside the house. We had a cloudy night tonight and we could not see what he was reacting too, but what ever it was it was a signefagent amount of time for what ever was happening up in the sky above the could be going on there. He must hear a sound out of human hearing range is why I think he whines at them. The dogs are known for their hearing range for high pitch sounds.
Summary: cloudy night all I could see was a glow in SW sky
